It’s my fault

43
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,000
Xiao Chengjing

44
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:07,159
It’s my fault for not giving you the ability to love

45
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,159
Your so-called love is truly touching

46
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,520
If you don’t come back

47
