51
00:03:51,719 --> 00:03:52,520
Yan Ying,

52
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,319
I hope you understand,

53
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,520
you are not only a female general,

54
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,719
