76
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,199
I will never forget you again.

77
00:06:46,439 --> 00:06:47,839
I will remember you forever.

78
00:06:49,199 --> 00:06:49,800
So,

79
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:52,839
