Please, don't die

104
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,120
Yan Ying

105
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:42,200
Yan Ying

106
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:56,000
Why is this happening

107
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,360
Why

108
00:09:27,879 --> 00:09:28,639
This time

109
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:30,240
We will make history

110
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:32,360
With an entirely new attempt

111
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:35,440
Combining Galactic Chronicles with VR

112
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:36,919
In VR

113
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,600
